This software is provided for educational purposes and authorized security
testing only. The author (G4MEOVER18) assumes no liability and is not
responsible for any misuse or damage caused by this program.

Using this tool against systems or networks without explicit written permission
from the owner is illegal. In Germany (and most jurisdictions) unauthorized
port scanning and network probing may violate:

  - § 202a StGB (Ausspähen von Daten / Unauthorized data access)
  - § 202b StGB (Abfangen von Daten / Data interception)
  - § 303b StGB (Computersabotage / Computer sabotage)

The Computer Fraud and Abuse Act (CFAA) in the United States, the Computer
Misuse Act in the United Kingdom, and similar laws in other countries.

YOU are responsible for your own actions. Always obtain written authorization
before scanning any system or network you do not own.

